								<br>
							    <ul>
								<li><strong>Note !</strong><br>In order to run a scan as a parallel scan,a user needs to specify a queue name in the queue name field and further more a user needs to put the same queue name in the config file <br>
								</li><li>Config file is a simple text file "config.txt" which needs to be placed in the root of directory of the web application under test.<br></li>
								<li>The exact location of where to place the config.txt file is technology dependent ,and to get the exact idea of where to place the config file click here :<br></li>
								<br><li><strong><b>Note : Once the scan is completed (which is run in parallel),its very important for the user to clear off the contents of the config file. </b></strong></li>
								</ul>
							    
							   </font>
							 
